| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4360 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 399ba1f5-4f06-562b-b9c4-ced2fbd175c7"
